The scripts in here can be used to create specific appliances.  They install
the necessary software and go through initial configuration steps.

Legend:

ms - EMail server using postfix, mysql, postfixadmin and dovecot
mx - MX server with antivirus and antispam filtering (inbound email)
backupmx - Backup MX server with antivirus filtering (inbound email)
mo - Email relay for sending emails (outbound email)
zenoss - Network management server
